title: Bitcoin rejects at key $93.5K as Fed rate-cut bets meet 'strong' bear case
description: Bitcoin price action fell back toward $90,000 on strong US jobs data as BTC ignored Fed rate-cut optimism, failing to flip the yearly open to support.
content:
Bitcoin (BTC) slipped from the 2025 yearly open into Thursdays Wall Street trading session as markets reacted to US jobs data.
